{"tid":469343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖）美單親母亂倫有前科 以死逼子女結婚","createTime":"2017-11-15T08:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T09:10:40.000Z","uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04d9978de1554a6daa2dbeaa2cf7b9deb5c7916f","tid":469343,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/160512_6e96206fbbb8bc472d7b89f41b2d4e8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F160512_6e96206fbbb8bc472d7b89f41b2d4e8a.jpg&h=98db2826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】美國奧克拉荷馬州26歲女子米絲蒂（Misty Spann），因與母親相戀亂倫罪名成立，早前被判緩刑十年，母親將在明年一月受審。原來這位「非常母親」有亂倫前科，之前曾跟自己長子結過婚，幼子控訴母親死威脅哥哥和姐姐跟她結婚。<br />\n<br />\n　　44歲的帕特里夏（Patricia Spann）早年失去三名子女撫養權，全部交由前夫母親撫養，直至三年前才與現年26歲的女兒米絲蒂（Misty Spann）相認。<br />\n<br />\n　　兩人重逢後一拍即合迅速撻着，其後更決定註冊結婚。帕特里夏稱，女兒出生證明上沒有寫上母親名字，認為兩人婚姻並不違法。然而這段不倫關係後被兒童福利調查機構揭發，米蒂斯近日被當局以亂倫罪判緩刑。<br />\n<br />\n　　警方調查後更發現，原來帕特里夏早在08年就曾與自己長子喬迪（Jody Spann）結婚，後被證實是亂倫關係。帕特里夏辯稱，當年是為阻止兒子當兵才假結婚，但與女兒結婚是真心的。但據帕特里夏的幼子科迪（Cody Spann）透露，他的哥哥姐姐是被逼才與母親結婚的。<br />\n<br />\n　　科迪稱，帕特里夏曾於07年以朋友身份出現在他們面前，完全不知對方是自己親生母親。後來哥哥喬迪與她的感情變得十分親暱，等帕特里夏回奧克拉荷馬州後，祖母才告訴他們帕特里夏是他們親生母親：「我的哥哥很痛苦，很想要離開她，但被威脅如果分手她就會殺了他。」<br />\n<br />\n　　據了解，帕特里夏與喬迪婚姻在2010年宣告無效，之後將興趣轉移到米絲蒂身上，並也曾以死威脅她。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E5%96%AE%E8%A6%AA%E6%AF%8D%E4%BA%82%E5%80%AB%E6%9C%89%E5%89%8D%E7%A7%91-%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%BB%E9%80%BC%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A-114300091.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E6%25AF%258D%25E4%25BA%2582%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25A7%2591-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%2580%25BC%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%25A9%259A-114300091.html&d=ywWURTQq08Fzn72WMUz%2FuZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f1f01872\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E7%BE%8E%E5%96%AE%E8%A6%AA%E6%AF%8D%E4%BA%82%E5%80%AB%E6%9C%89%E5%89%8D%E7%A7%91-%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%BB%E9%80%BC%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E7%B5%90%E5%A9%9A-114300091.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/160928_3b5977e065ce803488590d6f25cca7ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F160928_3b5977e065ce803488590d6f25cca7ae.jpg&h=160511ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dcab01ad307f72c734605716d8d8b4f3ba0536b","tid":469343,"uid":12569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:16:29.000Z","msg":"Cls新聞"},{"pid":"8829284000ed5851ddb6f8b9f9c08788ac93df39","tid":469343,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/161714_6ccb673219c230169d74e8a15af170dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F161714_6ccb673219c230169d74e8a15af170dd.jpg&h=c4f6a650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/162026_d31edcf035583ad7dbdd1b204b3c0fe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F162026_d31edcf035583ad7dbdd1b204b3c0fe5.jpg&h=2b2d06d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"245ba3da8b59a3a4bc6664c3c9cab79fac573db6","tid":469343,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"同完自己個仔結婚又同個女結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c2988333ddaff86a4294b28d51c06289b5a822","tid":469343,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同完自己個仔結婚又同個女結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15